  "subject": "Add MaxRAMPercentage=50% JVM default to Dockerfile",
  "commit_message": "Add MaxRAMPercentage=50% JVM default to Dockerfile\n\nWithout explicit MaxRAMPercentage, the JVM defaults to 25% of\ncontainer memory for heap while non-heap grows unconstrained.\nThis pod was observed at 438Mi/512Mi — OOM risk. Setting 50%\nprovides a balanced default that works with the increased\ncontainer limits from OOM-3391.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4350\nChange-Id: I5a8ee981e2d286f206256b1859616ed3267de7eb\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
